config EXOTICBALANCE
	bool "ExoticBalance IRQ Load Logger"
	default y
	help
	  Enables ExoticBalance, a custom IRQ load logger with GUI toggle support.
	  This module provides per-CPU IRQ counting and logs imbalance.
	  Toggle will appear in Franco Kernel Manager (/sys/module/exoticbalance/parameters/enabled).